Your project CANNOT be a reupload/reshare!HOW IT WILL BE JUDGED: Qucchia Wars will only have one judge: @qucchia. The entry will be rated using 7 aspects: Concept, Art, Smoothness, Coding, Theme, Sound and Setup. Each aspect of the entry will be rated out of 5, making a maximum score of 35.
